{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idbd57295d-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s5515"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5515"},"text":"§ 5515.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Use of publicly assisted housing by Secretary in demonstrations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary shall make appropriate use of publicly assisted housing and particularly low-rent housing assisted under the United States Housing Act of 1937 [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1437"},"text":"42 U.S.C. 1437","children":[],"tail":" et seq.] in demonstrating solar heating systems and combined solar heating and cooling systems under this subchapter."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idbd57295e-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/409/s17"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–409, § 17","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1974-09-03"},"text":"Sept. 3, 1974","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/88/1078"},"text":"88 Stat. 1078","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idbd57295f-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idbd572960-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idbd572961-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The United States Housing Act of 1937, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1937-09-01/ch896"},"text":"act Sept. 1, 1937, ch. 896","children":[],"tail":", as revised generally by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/383/tII/s201/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–383, title II, § 201(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1974-08-22"},"text":"Aug. 22, 1974","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/88/653"},"text":"88 Stat. 653","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to chapter 8 (§ 1437 et seq.) of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1437"},"text":"section 1437 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
